title: Jewelry Design Archive - 1000's of Designs - Manufacturer Catalo
description:
This is a catalog from a jeweler/metals caster on Philadelphia's Jeweler's Row. A stock archive of a century's worth of engagement rings, wedding bands, fashion rings and designer jewelry for made-to-order pieces. Each picture has corresponding pennyweight and catalog number for its rubber mold.

These guys are pretty awesome so if you see something you like, I'm sure they would appreciate your business :)

A page by page .jpg album version is available at http://imgur.com/a/uR4O9
